public class ConstrainedDistanceJBParameterEditor
extends DoubleParameterEditor

Title: ConstrainedDistanceJBEditor
Description: Special ParameterEditor for editing Constrained DistanceJBParameters. The widget is a NumericTextField so that only numbers can be typed in. When hitting or moving the mouse away from the NumericField, the value will change back to the original if the new number is outside the constraints range. The constraints also appear as a tool tip when you hold the mouse cursor over the NumericTextField
